				<td colspan="2"><span>Im still fairly new and all. I have heard and read about ppl doing raids and getting raid only items. What exactly is a &quot;raid&quot; and how do you get &quot;raid only&quot; items. My guild on Morden Rasp has done a few since I have become a member and most of them are  a much higher lvl then me so i havent done them yet. Im sure it is worth it because of the raid only items...but I'm still confused on this whole thing. Please dont flame me for this....noob question.</span></td>
