				<td colspan="2"><span>we only flame those who flame us   <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-5.gif" border="0" alt="Wink" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
we are bards we should joke more.
<br />

<br />
Anyways. Raid is where people gather together to kill a mob, now this mob doesn't always have to be a raid mob. Sometimes raid kill normal mob and get normal loot too.
<br />

<br />
The main thing about &quot;raid only loot&quot; you are talking about is those mobs that require a lot of people to kill and sometimes take some strat because they do odd things. And once it dies it drops things that normal mobs won't drop, so people call it raid only loot.
<br />

<br />
As too how the loot is distributed is up for debate. But usually is the DKP system. The more raid you join the more you deserve some items I guess.</span></td>
